---
---
<section id="formularios" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-floral-white/40 border-t border-b border-dust-grey/40 relative">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Copy Column (Left) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-700 font-mono">Editor WYSIWYG En Vivo</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight text-balance leading-tight">
          Personaliza tu canal con identidad de marca
        </h3>
        <p class="text-base text-slate-700 text-pretty leading-relaxed">
          Haz que el canal de denuncias se sienta parte nativa de tu ecosistema. Modifica secciones, carga el logo corporativo de tu empresa, ajusta la paleta de colores y configura preguntas específicas mediante nuestro constructor visual en tiempo real. 
        </p>

        <!-- Core Customization Aspects -->
        <div class="space-y-6 pt-2">
          <!-- Aspect 1 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a3 3 0 003 3h7a2 2 0 012 2v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-8a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Marca y Colores Corporativos</h4>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mt-1">
                Alinea el canal con tus colores y tipografías. Sube el logotipo de tu empresa y el sistema adaptará de manera inteligente los tonos de los botones, fondos y textos para una transición sin fricción desde tu sitio web.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Aspect 2 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zm0 8a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2zm0 8a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Personalización por Secciones</h4>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mt-1">
                Divide el reporte en pasos estructurados (Identificación, Descripción, Adjuntos) para no abrumar al usuario. Organiza campos de texto, campos obligatorios y reglas lógicas dinámicas según el tipo de caso.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Aspect 3 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Experiencia WYSIWYG Interactiva</h4>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mt-1">
                Edita etiquetas, añade aclaraciones y reorganiza elementos simplemente haciendo clic en ellos o arrastrándolos. El resultado que ves en pantalla es exactamente el que verán tus trabajadores al acceder.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- WYSIWYG Form Builder Mockup Column (Right) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 relative reveal reveal-delay-200">
        
        <!-- Background decorative glow -->
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-almond-cream/15 rounded-3xl blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

        <!-- Browser Address Bar Mockup -->
        <div class="w-full bg-white border border-dust-grey rounded-t-xl px-4 py-2.5 flex items-center justify-between gap-3 shadow-xs border-b-0">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-400/80"></span>
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400/80"></span>
            <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-400/80"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow max-w-md bg-floral-white/80 border border-dust-grey/70 rounded-md py-1 px-3 text-[11px] text-slate-500 text-center font-mono select-none truncate">
            https://admin.confialine.com/builder/canal-etico
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-600 font-medium">Modo Edición</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main WYSIWYG Panel Interface -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-dust-grey rounded-b-xl shadow-md p-4 sm:p-5 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-12 gap-5 relative overflow-hidden">
          
          <!-- Left Panel: Settings & Branding Options (4 cols) -->
          <div class="sm:col-span-4 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-3 space-y-4 select-none">
            
            <!-- Branding Tabs -->
            <div class="flex border-b border-slate-200 pb-1.5 justify-between">
              <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-800 font-bold font-mono">Estructura</span>
              <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-700 font-bold font-mono border-b-2 border-emerald-600">Apariencia</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Configuration Options -->
            <div class="space-y-3.5">
              
              <!-- 1. Logo Customization -->
              <div class="space-y-1.5">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Logotipo Marca</span>
                <div class="bg-white border border-dust-grey/65 rounded-lg p-2 flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 truncate">
                    <div class="h-5 w-5 rounded bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 flex-shrink-0">
                      <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-700 truncate font-mono">logo_corporativo.png</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[9px] text-emerald-600 font-bold font-mono flex-shrink-0">OK</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2. Brand Colors selector -->
              <div class="space-y-1.5">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Colores de Interfaz</span>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-5 gap-1 pt-0.5">
                  <button class="h-5 w-full rounded bg-emerald-700 border-2 border-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center text-white" aria-label="Emerald theme">
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                  <button class="h-5 w-full rounded bg-indigo-700 border border-slate-200" aria-label="Indigo theme"></button>
                  <button class="h-5 w-full rounded bg-slate-800 border border-slate-200" aria-label="Charcoal theme"></button>
                  <button class="h-5 w-full rounded bg-amber-700 border border-slate-200" aria-label="Amber theme"></button>
                  <button class="h-5 w-full rounded bg-[#2c1d11] border border-slate-200" aria-label="Brown theme"></button>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 3. Form Sections manager -->
              <div class="space-y-1.5">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Secciones Formulario</span>
                <div class="space-y-1 text-[10px] text-slate-650 font-medium">
                  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 px-2 py-1.5 rounded flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>1. Detalles Suceso</span>
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200/80 px-2 py-1.5 rounded flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span>2. Pruebas y Evidencia</span>
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 px-2 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="font-bold">+ Añadir Sección</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 4. Drag fields -->
              <div class="space-y-1.5 pt-1">
                <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block font-mono">Arrastrar Nuevos Campos</span>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-1.5 text-[9px] text-slate-700">
                  <div class="bg-white border border-dust-grey/70 rounded p-1.5 flex items-center gap-1 cursor-grab hover:border-slate-400">
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h7" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Texto</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white border border-dust-grey/70 rounded p-1.5 flex items-center gap-1 cursor-grab hover:border-slate-400">
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>Opción</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Center Panel: Live WYSIWYG Form Preview (8 cols) -->
          <div class="sm:col-span-8 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[380px] relative shadow-2xs">
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <!-- Live Preview Header with Corporate branding logo mockup -->
              <div class="pb-3 border-b border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between">
                <!-- Branding logo preview inside form -->
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <div class="h-7 px-2.5 rounded bg-slate-900 text-white text-[9px] font-bold tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1 font-mono uppercase">
                    <!-- Fictional Client Corporate Logo simulation (Brand Color applied) -->
                    <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
                    Globex Corp
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[8px] text-slate-400 border-l border-slate-200 pl-2 font-mono">Vista Previa Real</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Step Indicator -->
                <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-emerald-800 bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-100">Sección 1: Detalles</span>
              </div>

              <!-- Form Preview Fields (WYSIWYG layout with hover controls) -->
              <div class="space-y-3.5">
                
                <!-- Field 1: Category with WYSIWYG Hover Border & controls representation -->
                <div class="bg-floral-white/50 border-2 border-emerald-600 rounded-lg p-3 relative group transition">
                  <!-- Active selection bubble tools -->
                  <div class="absolute -top-3.5 right-3 bg-emerald-600 text-white text-[8px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded flex items-center gap-1.5 shadow-sm font-mono">
                    <span class="font-bold">Editar Campo</span>
                    <button class="hover:text-emerald-200">
                      <svg class="h-2.5 w-2.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" /></svg>
                    </button>
                  </div>

                  <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
                    <label class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 block">1. Seleccione la categoría de su reporte</label>
                    <span class="text-[8px] text-red-500 font-bold uppercase">Requerido</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full bg-white border border-dust-grey/50 rounded px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[10px] text-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center font-medium">
                    <span>Acoso Laboral / Maltrato</span>
                    <svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Field 2: Description of facts -->
                <div class="border border-slate-200/80 bg-white rounded-lg p-3 relative hover:border-slate-350 transition group">
                  <!-- Quick controls overlay shown on subtle workspace hover -->
                  <div class="absolute top-2 right-2 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-100 transition flex gap-1">
                    <button class="h-4.5 w-4.5 rounded bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-200">
                      <svg class="h-2.5 w-2.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" /></svg>
                    </button>
                    <button class="h-4.5 w-4.5 rounded bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 hover:text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50">
                      <svg class="h-2.5 w-2.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" /></svg>
                    </button>
                  </div>

                  <label class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-900 block mb-1">2. Describa detalladamente los hechos sucedidos</label>
                  <div class="w-full bg-slate-50/60 border border-dust-grey/40 rounded px-2.5 py-2.5 text-[10px] text-slate-400 min-h-[50px]">
                    Ingresa detalles específicos: fechas, nombres y lo sucedido...
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Drop Target Slot Area (Dashed green WYSIWYG insert point) -->
                <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-emerald-400/80 bg-emerald-50/15 rounded-lg p-3 text-center text-[9px] text-emerald-800 font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 animate-pulse relative">
                  <svg class="h-4.5 w-4.5 text-emerald-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Arrastre el bloque aquí para insertar elemento</span>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- WYSIWYG Canvas controls -->
            <div class="pt-3 border-t border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-[8.5px] text-slate-400 font-mono">Tema aplicado: <strong class="text-emerald-700 font-bold uppercase">Corporativo Verde</strong></span>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <button class="px-2.5 py-1 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-medium rounded hover:bg-slate-50 transition border border-slate-200">
                  Descartar
                </button>
                <button class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white text-[10px] font-semibold rounded shadow-2xs transition">
                  Guardar y Publicar
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Dragging Animation overlay (Simulating Carga de Archivos drag in progress) -->
          <div class="absolute top-[48%] left-[28%] sm:left-[36%] rotate-2 bg-white border-2 border-emerald-600 rounded-xl p-3 shadow-xl text-[10px] text-slate-800 w-44 sm:w-48 flex items-center gap-2 pointer-events-none z-30 animate-bounce">
            <div class="h-5 w-5 rounded bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0L8 8m4-4v12" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow truncate">
              <strong class="font-bold block text-[9.5px]">Carga de Evidencia</strong>
              <span class="text-[7.5px] text-slate-400 block truncate">Insertar en sección 1</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Click pointer finger hand cursor -->
            <svg class="h-5.5 w-5.5 text-emerald-600 absolute -bottom-3 -right-2 transform rotate-12 drop-shadow-md" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M7 11h-1v-2c0-.55.45-1 1-1s1 .45 1 1v2zm4 0h-1v-3c0-.55.45-1 1-1s1 .45 1 1v3zm4 0h-1v-3c0-.55.45-1 1-1s1 .45 1 1v3zm4 0h-1v-5c0-.55.45-1 1-1s1 .45 1 1v5zm-14.7 3.3l4.7 4.7c.37.37.88.58 1.41.58h6.59c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-5.2c0-.38-.22-.72-.56-.88l-4.5-2.2c-.37-.18-.8-.11-1.1.18l-1.84 1.84v-4.14c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2s-2 .9-2 2v9.38l-3.32-1.66c-.46-.23-1.01-.13-1.37.24-.37.37-.4.96-.06 1.36z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Float badge "UX de confianza" -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-5 right-6 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-200 p-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-md flex items-center gap-2 max-w-[210px] z-20">
          <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600">
            <svg class="h-4.5 w-4.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-600 leading-tight">
            <strong class="text-slate-900 font-bold block">UX Centrada en Confianza</strong>
            Personalizado y seguro
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
